{"tid":1013663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 洗街灰塵弄髒愛車　車主狂罵清潔工","createTime":"2019-02-08T13:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T09:26:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9df835cae83c7e273b9f8bc6700a5de2824be062","tid":1013663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"大角咀有車主將愛車泊在街邊後，在網上發貼怒斥清潔工洗街令車輛染上灰塵，結果反引來網民圍插。<br />\n<br />\n該車主在Facebook群組「我長大於大角咀」發貼大呻，當日有幾名清潔工人圍封鐵樹街一段行人路，以水槍沖刷街道。他頓時大怒：「赤口X咗佢哋幾下，個個啲車新年先打完蠟洗晒車，你哋一洗地就將啲泥塵打番晒上架車」！<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，不少網民反罵車主：「又洗車又打蠟就唔好擺街啦」、「過年唔洗得街咩」、「睇相都見人哋用水槍幫你沖番啦」、「有好多舖係過年先唔開，依家唔洗幾時洗」。現時貼文已被刪去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/bkn-20190208153504604-0208_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190208%2Fbkn-20190208153504604-0208_00822_001.html&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=6908552b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190208/bkn-20190208153504604-0208_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0fc18df57b0c4af334a37c447da75bcf050a7fe5","tid":1013663,"uid":71133,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T13:59:52.000Z","msg":"有錢買車冇錢泊車，香港最撚多呢d乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7d4abac9330b43d1bc0265d2601ce148ec5da3","tid":1013663,"uid":84903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T14:02:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留番d錢洗下你把臭口好過喇仆街"},{"pid":"81715fbd12158ca643b668b52263825fadb31c48","tid":1013663,"uid":50835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T14:04:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 咁撚巴閉點解要泊係街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c80c969079ad7cded0bdaa860033025485bf4aa","tid":1013663,"uid":71768,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T14:12:24.000Z","msg":"之前都試過 電單車件啡令衫全泥蹟<br />\n<br />\n呻2句就算，泊街真係預佐"},{"pid":"387e2677f61ddc9c913